Scheduled for 1.3
=================

* ChanServ will maintain MLOCK +k channels (but will set them +s when no other
  users are in them).
* Add SPLIT Awareness - if user was recognized before, they are on rejoin.
* Re-Write the DELETION functions of some routines (AKICK and ACCESS in
  particular) to accept MASK deletion (like AKILL currently does).
* Nick Linking - Shared Access List, and all other details (also stay
  IDENTIFIED if you change nicks to another of your equivilant nicks).
  (Indipendant "Registered" and "Last On" times (Last On updating MAIN)).

Scheduled for whenever
======================

* A way to send commands to the services (especially OperServ) from shell.
* Do something about repeated password failures.
